summary: NPC located outside of Whiterun player home, and on the deck of the ship in Solitude docks.
descriptionHtml:
NPC located outside of Whiterun player home, and on the deck of the ship in Solitude docks.
He just stands there..... or you can kill him and get his awesome gear for free.
